Class UserDao

java.lang.Object
aor.fpbackend.dao.AbstractDao<UserEntity>
aor.fpbackend.dao.UserDao
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class UserDao extends AbstractDao<UserEntity>
UserDao class provides data access operations for UserEntity.

This class implements methods to perform CRUD operations and custom queries related to users in the database. It extends the AbstractDao class to inherit generic data access operations and adds specific methods for user management.
